\id PHM - Migabac NT; 9 Sep 2011 1st draft 
\h Filemon 
\toc1 Poldi Filemon Yele Hibi Kwelengkewec 
\toc2 Filemon 
\toc3 Film 
\mt2 Poldi  
\mt1 Filemon  
\mt2 Yele Hibi Kwelengkewec  
\is1 Mimi-yegeng yowa  
\ip Filemon ye ngic monic woc-wiyacine homacneholecti Kolosi taonka gawec. Ye Yesu ngagesingkeme Yesule habu yenge yele macka kpaduckeibong. Ailu ye Pol agoine gawec. Filemon yele kwelec kwekweine monic, wacine Onesimus, ye Filemon hegile hikelu Pol bafuwawec. Bafuwame Poldi Yesule siduc edome ngagesingkelu ye bafickewec.  
\ip Filemon nga Onesimus yeke ngaba ingucne gaiboc. Inguc gaboc Poldi baficepanogale hibi yago kwelengkewec. Yesu homackacni gboliyelu honocmengka feme hifa 32 ngama ingucne motome, hibi yago kwelengkewec.  
\c 1  
\s1 Hibile molic-molic yowa  
\p
\v 1 Na Poldi \w Kristo\w* \w Yesule|lemma="Yesu"\w* siduc mibe yegengkeme muc-macka locnubong ngiyegabac. Ailu \w ngic hae-gbanonggeng|lemma="ngic hae-gba"\w* Timoti, noki hibi yago lobec Filemon gala fugac. Ga bole moniyangnonggec aime kwelenonggecti gale angac ngagelu gagabelec.  
\v 2 Sengnonggeng Afia nga Sugucnele bole-baba ngic agononggec Arkipus, ye nga Yesule habu Filemonte macka kpaduckecaigaing, hibi yago ngengele momoc logabelec.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 4:17; 2Tim 2:3\x*  
\v 3 Mamacnonggeng Wapong nga Sugucnenonggeng Yesu Kristo, yekele kwele-madic nga kwele-mogungtowadi ngengela fadaic.   
\s1 Kwele-madic yowa  
\p
\v 4-5 Filemon, ga Sugucne Yesu ngagesingkelu Wapongte bingec sasawa yengele kwelegonedi angac ngageyelecaigic, gale siduc inguc ngagecaigabac. Ilec ailu mimilocna gale ngagelu damengsoc Wapong kwele-madic edolu gagabac.  
\v 6 Ga ngage-ngagesingka nongeholec momoc taockelu Kristoholec wetackelu gagabeleng. Ilec Kristole wiyac madicne sasawa bagabeleng, yogo sasawa gagi ngage-motocte milockecaigabac.  
\v 7 Ngic hae-gbane, kwelegonedi Wapongte bingec yenge ago bacebalu angac ngageyelelu kwelengineng hole-gboliyecaigamec. Yengela inguc nganiibale aibabagone yogodi basanangnume homacnehac beliyegabac.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt 2Kor 7:4\x*   
\s1 Onesimus  
\p
\v 8 Ilec ailu Kristoholec wetacke galu bole geleicne yogo badamecte, na ngagelu ung-yowa yogo nalic edocgudacte.  
\v 9 Aime sifu kweledi angac ngagegelelu aibaba madicna domalu yowa ulucnedi sanangne milocgudacte. Aime na Pol, ngic dandangngine yanguctihac Kristo Yesule ailu muc-macka gagabac.  
\v 10 Na madecne monic yele yowale sanangne milocgudacte. Na muc-macka galu Yesule siduc micnobe ngagesingkeme mamacinele silic ingucne fikelu gaiba, wacine Onesimus.\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Onesimus wacine fungine yogo babaficineholec.\f* \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Kol 4:9; 1Kor 4:15\x*  
\v 11 Ye esecne molickelu gaholec gawec, iwa mi baficgulu gawec. Nga yakumacbac ga nga na nokilec momochac baficnupalu gadaicte.  
\v 12 Naneicne kwelene salegabac ingucne ye salebe gala hefaliyelu fudaicte.  
\v 13 \w Siduc Madicnele|lemma="Siduc Madicne"\w* ailu muc-macka gaebewa, yedi gale mac balu naholec yawa galu baficnudecka ingucne, yogo nalic aidec inguc ngageiba.  
\v 14 Aime gagi mi miyengka nani ye kwelenele sebilebe hegiledameckale ailu, hegileiba. Aime nale angacte miyac, geicne angac balaibelu aibaba madicne ainelecte salebe fudaicte.   
\s1 Kwelec kwekwe ngic  
\p
\v 15 Onesimus ye ngage-ngagesingkolec agogone gaholec mac-fung ganogale mecne molickelu hegilecguwec.  
\v 16 Hegilecgulu kwelec kwekwe ngic silicka hatacmac mi kwesidaicte, miyac. Ye yakumac ngic hae-gbanonggeng kwele-angacka gacaigac. Na yele ingucbenang ngagegabac. Aime yedi gale kwelec kwekwe aigac. Nga ngage-ngagesingka Sugucnele ailu ye momochac ngic hae-gbagone aigac, aibaba yogo wiyac feicne.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1Tim 6:2\x*  
\v 17 Ilec ailu ga ngageng nokilec ago-ago aigabelecka, Onesimus fudaicte, ye inguchac nani fube na aineledameckalesoc silicine ingucnehac yele angacgume badamec.  
\v 18 Aime yedi yefe ewalilu wiyacgone monic basowalewecka, me yele tofa monic gala fagacka, yogo sasawa hegileng nale wacka fadaic.  
\v 19 Na Pol neicne molenedi hibi yago kwelengkegabac. Na tofa yogo ameine badugeledacte. Aime na Yesule siduc milu edocgube ngagesingkeing. Ilec geicne gagale amegone nala fagac, yogolec yowabac mi migabac.   
\s1 Bole aling nga wenac-madic  
\p
\v 20 Ga foinac ngic hae-gbane, Sugucnenonggeng Kristole ailu na baficnung kwelene hole-gboliyedaic.  
\v 21 Aime yowa ngagelu balaibedamecte yogo fagac, yogo ngagepangkelu hibi yago kwelengkegelegabac. Aime Onesimusle migabac, yogo gagi taockelu hatacmac aidamecte, yogo ngagegabac.   
\p
\v 22 Ailu monic yanguc ngagesilu wangec gagabac, ngengele mimilocnginengte ailu muc-mackacni bamoctocnubong ngengela fudacte. Ilec nale mac kweline monic bamockedamec.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Filp 1:25; 2:24\x*   
\p
\v 23 Na Epafasholec noke momoc Kristo Yesule ailu muc-macka gagabelec, yedi gale wenac-madic lome fugac.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Kol 1:7\x*  
\v 24 Ngic naholec galu bole momochac bacaigabeleng Mareko, Aristakus, Demas nga Luka, yenge inguchac wenac-madicngineng lobong fugac.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Kol 4:10-12,14; 1Tim 4:10-11\x*  
\v 25 Sugucnenonggeng Yesu Kristole kwele-madicti asunginang fadaic. Yogo foinac.   